713207f-b.text:
View 1;
West 44th Street, from west 43rd Street, across parking space and Tenth and Eleventh Avenues, north showing Houbicant building.
September 4, 1940.
View 2;
West 44th Street, north west corner of Eleventh Avenue looking westwards, ware-house docks may be seen at end of street
on Hudson River.
View 3;
West 44th Street, north side looking eastwards from Eleventh Avenue.
P.L.Speer.
NO REPRODUCTIION.  September 4, 1940.

